Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.97,0:00:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your Ponyville\NChronicle right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fan-tizzy-astic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just love to read about happy\Nhappenings and it's always good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a pony in\Nthe know, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's so much to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. Seems like a bunch of\Nboring hooey to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does "NEW SHRUBBERY\NIN CASTLE GARDEN"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,sound like boring\Nhooey to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Snooze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"PARASPRITE INFESTATION IN\NFILLYDELPHIA ERADICATED"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhhh. Another day, another\Nparasprite hype story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Noodles named official\Nfood of Whinnyapolis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Author A.K. Yearling\Nannounces retirement!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cloudsdale election\Nheating up for candidate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in favor of\Ncooling it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT? Let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew you were so\Ninto politics, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It CAN'T be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have never have picked\Nnoodles as the official food
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of Whinnyapolis, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But... here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that the greatest author...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and secret pony\Nadventurer of all time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A.K. Yearling... is retiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A.K. Yearling just\Nretired, like, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she wants visitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.79,0:02:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, the A.K. Yearling\NI know would never quit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and retire out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.43,0:02:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Something could\Nbe really wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to make\Nsure she's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.... you're not just trying\Nto make sure she writes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,more Daring Do\Nbooks, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wouldn't\Nhurt either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.. maybe she's not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she went to the\Neditor-in-chief of the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville Chronicle to\Ncorrect the misprint they've made!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie: Nope. She's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she's right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,looking all sad and alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A.K!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's sighing with\Nthe weight of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's hanging her\Nhead in utter despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she's shaking her hoof\Nand cursing the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,like nothing could ever\Npossibly be the same again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why oh why did this\Nhappen to her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, that time\Nshe was just stretching. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A.K., it's us! Rainbow\NDash and Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Did somepony ransack\Nyour cottage again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and steal some ancient\Nmysterious relic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the key to saving\Nall of Equestria!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Sparky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's been stolen..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then is somepony blackmailing\Nyou and forcing you to retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause if they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So.. you're just quitting\Nand moving away!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,WHY. WOULD. YOU. DO. THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I already explained everything\Nto the Ponyville Chronicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Author A.K. Yearling\Nannounced yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that the next adventure novel\Nin her popular series,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,'Daring Do and the Curse\Nof the Pharaoh's Tomb'
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,will be her last.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yearling looks forward\Nto her retirement."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't\Nexplain anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It just says you're\Ngiving up writing stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But most ponies don't know that\Nyou actually are Daring Do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the\Nstories are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're REALLY saying\Nis that you're giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,being Daring Do, but\Nyou're not saying why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you don't\Nfeel like talking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that's A-OK, A.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As your friends, we\Ncompletely understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah. We just came to\Nmake sure you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's.. really why we wanted\Nto find out what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really\Nwant to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My last quest took me to a\Nvillage in Southern Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,where I started seeing.. these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"WAKE OF DESTRUCTION:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,DARING DO RUINS ENTIRE\NVILLAGE MARKETPLACE"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"DARE OR SCARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCAL ROGUE 'DARING DO'\NINVOLVED IN FRIGHTFUL FIASCO"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"DARING DO LEADS BULL INTO CHINA\NSHOP DURING HIGH SPEED CHASE--"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony I tried to\Nhelp is mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not mad\Nat A.K. Yearling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mad at\N"Daring Do".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't sell my books\Nin Southern Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The ponies there don't\Nknow who A.K. Yearling is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They only know Daring Do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and apparently she does\Nmore harm than good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess it's a good thing\Nyou look so different
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as A.K. Yearling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So all we have to\Ndo is go down there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and explain to these ponies that\Nnone of this stuff is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy-peazy-cheezy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just the thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...it{\i1} is{\i0} true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've always\Nbeen so focused
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,on saving priceless relics\Nand stopping the bad guys
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that.. I never really thought\Nabout the mess I leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you ARE in\Na tricky pickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. why is all this\Nhappening now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.. I guess ponies are\Nfinally fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I'm done with\Nadventures: having or writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For every one\Npony who's upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there must be at least a hundred\Nthat know you're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so, Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't we go visit\Nthis village "Somnambula"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and see for ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those articles seem to\Nmake it pretty clear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,how the villagers feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we go there, the ponies\Ncan tell you in person
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,just how much they\Nappreciate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And what a heap of rotten apple\Ncores these articles are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmmm! This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks just like that\Nvillage in your last book
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,where Daring Do recovers\Nthe Doomed Diadem
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from The Wild Bunch Gang
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,who chase after her\Nthrough the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It should.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I based that entire chapter\Non my experiences here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,in Somnambula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens? No\Nwait, don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I CHANGED MY MIND! TELL ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do thwarts Ahuizotl's\Nevil plot to separate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sister Crown Relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it wasn't for her, the\Nregion would be cursed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with eternal night and the\Nentire town of Somnambula
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,would have sunk\Ninto the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah Pssht! There's no\Nchance that these ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,don't think you're a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiya there, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping you could tell me\Nabout a pony named Daring Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear she's an awesome\Nadventure-pony hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's awesome, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome at destroying\Nponies' apple carts
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and priceless,\Nsacred statues!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Daring\NDo is a menace
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who destroys everything\Nshe touches!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.61,0:07:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do is the exact\Nopposite of a menace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. I tried to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming back here\Nwas a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, A.K.! So we\Npicked a bad example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just one angry pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Two angry ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never should\Nhave come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! We gotta\Nfollow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it really seemed like\Nshe doesn't want us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,cramping her saddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to convince her\Nthat ponies do appreciate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As her friend, I have to\Nmake sure she believes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. Look, Pinkie! It's\Nthe "Get On Inn".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do stays here all\Nthe time in her adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there must be\Nponies here who love Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they can help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose is telling me to\Nhelp myself to muffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo, she's fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A good evening\Nto you, Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We are but weary travelers who\Nhumbly wish to inquire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,on the status of a\Ncertain mare of intrigue
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,taking residence here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What in Southern Equestria\Nare you on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that\NDaring Do stays here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Not anymore, she doesn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time I rented\Nthat rascal a room,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,she was in a such a rush to\Nhigh-tail it outta here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,she didn't even pay her bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But--\NAfter that, a band of\Nruffians showed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroyed half the\Nrooms looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess she made them even\Nmore mad than she made me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. You've\Ngot it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! How do ya figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do was trying to\Nsave everypony from the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse of the Doomed\NDiadem of Xilati!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was only in a rush\Nbecause she had to get the crown
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,back to the Tiara of Teotlale\Nbefore the curse took effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chapter seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a tall tale to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And a hard one to believe now\Nthat I know Daring Do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is a scoundrel and a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year, ponies come to\Noffer precious glowpaz
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Sonmambula\Nstatue in the village
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,in hopes for a good future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why that poor fella had\Nhis glowpaz necklace
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,stolen by Daring Do\Njust yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,THERE'S A.K.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do RUINED our town and\Nstole our precious glowpaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to make sure that\Nif she turns up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony who's with me,\Nmeet at the statue tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Now I'm getting blamed for\Nthings I didn't even do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I steal from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They are SUPER BAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But... we're still\Nstaying the night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I already ate all\Nthe free mini muffins!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, A.K., after a\Ngood night's sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to fix\Nall of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be\Nhere, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is never\Ngoing to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is go up\Nthere and explain to everypony
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,how wrong they all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! And then I'll be\Nlike what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Easy-peazy-cheezy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is! The\Nremains of your--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean our\NSomnambula statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Daring Do has\Ndestroyed it, tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,where will we hang our glowpaz?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even have any glowpaz\Nbecause they were stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,by Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Daring Do would\Nnever steal anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And OK, she destroyed\Nyour statue,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was because she was\Ntrying to save you all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,from Ahuizotl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahuizotl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's about yay big?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Long neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Itty-bitty face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird claw thingy on his tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooo! Ooo! I know him!\NHe's a baddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, if Ahuizotl had gotten\Naway with the Doomed Diadem,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,your entire village would\Nhave been swallowed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a lot worse than\Nlosing some CRUMMY old statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This was not some\Ncrummy old statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the namesake\Nof our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to understand us,\Nyou must first understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Somnambula...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Long ago this village fell{\i0}\N{\i1} prey to an evil Sphinx{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} who demanded most{\i0}\N{\i1} of their crops.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Like her fellow villagers,{\i0}\N{\i1} Somnambula didn't have much,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} but she used what she had to{\i0}\N{\i1}keep others from giving up hope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The son of the{\i0}\N{\i1} Pharaoh, Prince Hisan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} was so moved by{\i0}\N{\i1} her compassion,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} that he decreed nopony{\i0}\N{\i1} would go hungry again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} But when Hisan stood{\i0}\N{\i1} up to the Sphinx,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the beast captured him, telling{\i0}\N{\i1} the Pharaoh the only way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to get Hisan back was to{\i0}\N{\i1} solve her riddle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Nopony would volunteer{\i0}\N{\i1} to save the prince.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Nopony except Somnambula.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sphinx gave her the riddle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I shine brightest in the dark.{\i0}\N{\i1} I am there but cannot be seen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} To have me costs you nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} To be without me costs{\i0}\N{\i1} you everything."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} As Somnambula thought{\i0}\N{\i1} of the hardship{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she and her fellow{\i0}\N{\i1} villagers had experienced,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she instantly{\i0}\N{\i1} knew the answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} "HOPE!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} She shouted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The Sphinx was so enraged, it{\i0}\N{\i1} seemed she might still refuse{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to release the prince,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} so Somnambula asked her{\i0}\N{\i1} for one more challenge,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} but if she{\i0}\N{\i1} accomplished it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} the Sphinx would leave{\i0}\N{\i1} from the kingdom forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The Sphinx quickly agreed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} asking only that Somnambula{\i0}\N{\i1} walk to the prince...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ... across a deep{\i0}\N{\i1} chasm, blindfolded!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Further, the Sphinx had{\i0}\N{\i1} cast a powerful spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} that prevented{\i0}\N{\i1} Somnambula from flying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Somnambula never lost HOPE!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} She knew she'd need to{\i0}\N{\i1} make a leap of faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to save the prince.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Guided by the sound{\i0}\N{\i1} of the prince's voice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she easily made it across.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The Pharaoh asked how{\i0}\N{\i1} Somnambula prevailed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and she explained that{\i0}\N{\i1} she had always hoped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} she could make things{\i0}\N{\i1} better for her people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and that hope{\i0}\N{\i1} had carried her through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} The Prince replaced the{\i0}\N{\i1} pearls Somnambula gave up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} with a string of Glowpaz.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And around her neck, they{\i0}\N{\i1} glowed bright enough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to light the entire kingdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Forever after, Glowpaz{\i0}\N{\i1} became our symbol of hope.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I had no idea how special\Nthe statue was to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Somnambula sounds like\Na pretty cool pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet if she were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd tell you how cool\NDaring Do is too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because they've both\Nfought to protect this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If Somnambula were here today,\Nshe would condemn Daring Do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for destroying yo--\NOUR symbol of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Daring Do ever do\Nto you to deserve all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only... everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Caballeron!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you,\Nher closest friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that Daring Do\Nwould not be far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I really do owe you for\Nleading her right to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't mean--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me\Nbreak Daring Do's spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,by destroying\Nher reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't have you running\Noff and telling her my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Caballeron?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... coming...\NRainbow... Dash...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I knew you'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I cause\Nmore trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't let anything\Nhappen to Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You care too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To the pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash: Somepony help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash: Somepony! Anypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Rainbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If my previous plan didn't cause\Nyou to give up, Daring Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then the shame of losing your\Ndear friend Rainbow Dash
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to the slime will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and that ancient magic\Nfrom the legend is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be no flying\Nin the pyramid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right! We'll never\Nget to her in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If this really is like\NSomnambula's story,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then we just have to\Nhave hope that we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we need more\Nthan hope, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a bridge in the story\Nand there's no bridge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but Rainbow\NDash is our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Somnambula. We\Nneed to make a leap of faith
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and hope that we can save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,PINKIE!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheeee! Hee hee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew we'd do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for reminding me to\Nnever give up hope, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm kinda hoping you\Nponies will untie me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,before we all take a bath\Nin bubbling green slime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast, Caballeron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU stole our glowpaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known you were\Njust trying to sully my name
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you'd be free to\Nsteal whatever you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course that was\Nthe plan, Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At first I just\Nwanted the Glowpaz...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I saw an opportunity to\Nwrite you out of the story
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,FOR GOOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the destruction\Nyou leave in your wake,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't take too much\Nto convince ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you were a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong, Caballeron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't let you\Nbreak my spirit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm never\Ngoing to give up hope
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can protect ponies\Nand ancient treasures
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,from miscreants like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember! She\Nruined your statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fools to\Nbelieve in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrr! You'll pay for this, Daring Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, OK that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for helping\Nme come to my senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are true friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just glad you're back\Nto your old self again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggle] Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad I realized that\Neven if you're fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for something good, you're still\Nresponsible for your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And if something bad happens\Nthat you didn't intend,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't give up hope\Nor lose faith in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! All ya gotta do\Nis make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to use that\Nin your next book!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think I will.
